FBIS4-53826 "dreas100_c_94003" FBIS-EAS-94-100 Daily Report 22 May 1994 North Korea Foreign Ministry Answer Distributed as UN Document Foreign Ministry Answer Distributed as UN Document SK2205085594 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0807 GMT 22 May 94 SK2205085594 Pyongyang KCNA English BFN [Text] Pyongyang, May 22 (KCNA) -- The answer of a spokesman for the DPRK Foreign Ministry dated May 14 as to the beginning of replacement of fuel rods at the 5 megawatt experimental nuclear power station in the DPRK was distributed on May 16 as official document S/1994/576 of the United Nations Security Council.
